snippet.title: Asuka 120% Excellent BURNING Fest [PS1] Story Mode
snippet.description:
## Like this video and subscribe my channel, it will help a lot! ##

New video of Asuka 120% saga, this 4th video is a remake for PS1 of the second game, that was released only for FM Towns, a japanese computer. This game has a lot of dialogues and is some sort of RPG, where we can do different choices in the story. It's a good game for those who understand Japanese, not my case. But I have followed a guide and I could finish the game. 

It's one of most obscure games of Asuka 120%, with just few videos with a complete longplay. Again, this was recorded from my old PS2, with retrocompatibility to PF1. Enjoy this video and I will see you next time.
